you take care
of all of them.

11:51.344 --> 11:55.715 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And so while -- what has
happened really is
because of the issue with
microcephaly, and

11:55.815 --> 12:01.688 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
