number of cases.

12:22.141 --> 12:27.013 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
There's no doubt that
microcephaly, or these
small heads, in newborns, as --
and small

12:27.113 --> 12:33.152 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
