occurring,

12:38.458 --> 12:40.326 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
where it's occurring.

12:40.426 --> 12:43.830 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right now, much of Brazil has
not been impacted.
