What we have
to do is look at where it's
going to unfold.

12:48.134 --> 12:53.072 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Just as an example, the
chikungunya virus,
which came into St. Martin in
December of

12:53.172 --> 12:58.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
2013, is still unfolding across
the Americas.
