Zika virus.

12:58.745 --> 13:02.248 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the next two years, we are
just going
to just see this continue wave
after wave

13:02.348 --> 13:04.150 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
