13:04.250 --> 13:11.691 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Dr. Michael
Osterholm of the University
of Minnesota, thank you very
much.

13:11.791 --> 13:27.373 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Sweden is
