14:38.277 --> 14:44.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Nazis and racists crossing the
street and
demonstrating against the
refugees arriving

14:45.051 --> 14:48.187 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
