14:48.287 --> 14:55.661 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: These are
right-wing vigilantes,
including football hooligans,
apparently attacking

14:55.762 --> 15:05.171 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
