where young Moroccans
hang out. Many have acquired a
reputation

15:05.271 --> 15:08.141 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
as petty criminals and
troublemakers.

15:08.241 --> 15:12.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The attack happened a few days
