at a young asylum seeker's
hostel in Western

15:12.979 --> 15:18.718 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Sweden. A 22-year-old worker,
Alexandra Mezher,
originally from Lebanon, was
stabbed to death,

15:18.818 --> 15:23.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
