who come here to Sweden have had
traumatic

15:46.179 --> 15:48.915 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
experiences, and there are no
simple answers.

15:49.015 --> 15:54.320 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Fredrik Hagberg
is a leading
member of a far-right activist
group called

15:54.420 --> 15:58.124 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
