and more immigrants than we can
take care

16:07.333 --> 16:13.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of is coming every day. The
violence is getting
more and more. Hatred against
Swedes, people

16:13.105 --> 16:18.611 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
