16:24.617 --> 16:27.286 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: It sounds like
you might
be advocating violence?

16:27.386 --> 16:32.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FREDRIK HAGBERG: No, not at all,
not at all.
Our movement has always stood
against violence,

16:33.059 --> 16:35.394 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
political violence, but I
believe in self-defense.

16:35.494 --> 16:44.837 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: And this is one
of his organization's
videos.

16:44.937 --> 16:46.305 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Are you Nazis?

16:46.405 --> 16:48.040 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
FREDRIK HAGBERG: No, not at all.

16:48.140 --> 16:50.076 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: How can you
