on one young
boy. This is just one of what
the police say

17:33.352 --> 17:39.191 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have been 5,000 incidents at
asylum centers
that they have been called to
attend.

17:39.292 --> 17:43.829 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anna Nellberg Dennis, deputy
chair of Sweden's
police union, says there have
been recent

17:43.930 --> 17:45.831 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
problems west of Stockholm in
