17:45.932 --> 17:48.768 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANNA NELLBERG DENNIS, Deputy
Chair, Swedish
Police Union: We were down on
our knees, work-wise

17:48.868 --> 17:53.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and workload-wise, already long
