18:38.551 --> 18:42.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAGNUS RANSTORP: There is some
recruitment
by Islamic extremists at train
stations.

18:42.922 --> 18:47.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Today, Sweden's
Interior
Minister Anders Ygeman was
trying to project

18:47.526 --> 18:49.195 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
