in Swedish policies.

20:06.205 --> 20:10.009 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TINA MORAD: We have built up our
reputation
internationally of being this
humanitarian

20:10.109 --> 20:14.613 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
