future.

20:22.922 --> 20:27.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Iraqi civil
servant Adel
Ali Qatani has decided to return
to Baghdad

20:28.060 --> 20:32.631 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
