more difficult
for refugees to bring over their
families.

20:32.731 --> 20:37.703 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ADEL ALI QATANI, Refugee
(through translator):
I see no solution. I can't wait
for three

20:37.803 --> 20:42.441 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
