adult. The laws
complicate matters.

20:46.579 --> 20:50.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Although I'm very grateful for
all the help
I have been given, I feel very
frustrated

20:50.349 --> 20:54.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
