uncertainty
the government is going through,
all these

20:54.320 --> 20:58.958 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
different changes. It's better
to return to
my family and endure the
hardship with them,

20:59.058 --> 21:00.960 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
