32:01.153 --> 32:05.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARCY DARNOVSKY, Center for
Genetics and Society:
Well, I think for people who are
in the situation

32:06.024 --> 32:10.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that has just been described,
